    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122050/extras/599c8d4551e7945c72a95dd86da85871.poster.avif?t=1766290719\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122050/extras/599c8d4551e7945c72a95dd86da85871.webm?t=1766290719\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122050/extras/599c8d4551e7945c72a95dd86da85871.mp4?t=1766290719\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>Welcome to Shadowbox Roulette!</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A mind game of <strong>ragebaiting</strong>, deception, reflexes, and sheer luck? Face off in a tense <strong>1v1</strong> where reading your opponent is the key to survival. But! Losing the <strong>shadowbox</strong> means stepping into <strong>Russian Roulette</strong>, where fates decides your destiny.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122050/extras/196adbc80e8ab95ca2fd0e643f8f1acb.avif?t=1766290719\" width=616 height=200 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Basically <strong>shadowboxing.</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solo: The player engages an AI opponent in a tense shadowboxing duel. Each turn is a battle of deception, look the way your opponent pointed, they earn the right to fire. Victory comes from landing a single decisive shot that knocks your opponent out.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiplayer: Still working on it. No rules. Feel free to mess around with your friends.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Given a lot of freedom, players can actually do whatever they want.</strong> </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"b